<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>OH, FOR A THOUSAND TONGUES!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mi sang tamtak in la sa'n au,
 Hukdampa chawian in; (2)
 Ka Pathien Lalpen lopina,
 A lungsietna lien chu (3)

[V2]
 2. Ei lungsiet Lalpa, ka Pathien,
 Hatna ei hun pie'n la; (2)
 Zie leisiet gam thim chung ahin,
 Na thu hilh viel dingin. (3)

[V3]
 3. Isu minin lauhna nawhmang,
 Lungkhamna ah ei nem; (2)
 Gilo di'n ngaihnawp um ahi,
 Hinna, damna, muonna. (3)

[V4]
 4. Leisiet zinmang Nuoisiehpa chun,
 Henkawl nangbang A sut; (2)
 A thisan gilopen thienna,
 Kei a di'n le thienna. (3)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>41</hymn_number>
</song>